platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Plenty of photo-editing apps come with filters, but Polarr can help you create your own. And you dont need the eye of a professional photographer, either. Thanks to instinctive touch controls and a ton of built-in filters to use as jumping-off points, its simple to tweak your images to get the perfect balance of colour and light. For the shutterbug pros, Polarr goes deep and allows fine adjustments to saturation, lens distortion and a whole lot of other settings that we dabblers just pretend to understand.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Advanced auto-enhance tools and filters to edit every detail of your photo.
